  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is planned to medicate oral T3(Liothyronine)to the patients who are planned to
      have OPCAB(off- pump coronary bypass graft surgery. The aim of this study was to assess the
      effects of oral triiodothyronine (T3) therapy on postoperative thyroid hormone
      concentrations, hemodynamic variables and outcomes in patients undergoing OPCAB in a
      randomized, controlled trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
